- [ ] Impersonation flow triggers audit logs and requires explicit confirmation; sessions revert to admin context upon exit.
- [ ] Admin Tools & Moderation can suspend/activate users, manage workspaces, and apply billing exceptions with proper audit trails.
- [ ] Exports and retention policies can be created/modified and reflect in Audit Logs.
- [ ] All endpoints enforce role-based access control and return appropriate error codes for unauthorized actions.
- [ ] UI adheres to the design system: cards, tables, charts, and navigation match the Visual Style section.

